aims-os-desktop-extras (2.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Carved out of aims-os-desktop to slim the live ISO
    from ~9 GB to ~4.5 GB. Holds the second browser (Chromium), creative
    tools (GIMP, Inkscape, Shotwell), Evolution mail, alternative shells
    and terminals, English LibreOffice helpers, and non-free codecs.

